UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1068
1 Be it resolved by the House of Representatives of the General Assembly of the
2 Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. The House of Representatives hereby honors the life and legacy of
4 José Martí and his impact on the city of Louisville and the Commonwealth of Kentucky.
5 Section 2. The House of Representatives encourages Jefferson County Public
6 Schools to recognize and honor José Martí by dedicating a future school in his name.
7 Section 3. The Clerk of the House of Representatives is directed to transmit a
8 copy of this Resolution to Representative Daniel Grossberg.
